extendedInfo.description: Graduate from Moron to Genius as you tap and twist your way through Section 3 of the hit game, The Moron Test! Master the game, then laugh as your friends and family struggle with these seemingly simple puzzles! The Moron Test is one of the App Store's most popular games of all time with millions of players worldwide, and now you can play Section 3 of the full game for free! Play now and experience why The Moron Test is an App Store favorite! The Moron Test - it's fun to FAIL! FEATURES: - Simple, addicting gameplay - Fun, tricky puzzles - Funny characters, sound effects, and music- You will LOVE watching your friends FAIL! Check out the full version of The Moron Test for even more fun!

reviews.title: Novelty Wearing Thin
reviews.comment: THERE\'S NOTHING WRONG WITH THE TEST: READ THE CLUES CAREFULLY AND THINK OUTSIDE THE BOX! I enjoyed Moron Tests no 1 & 2, but the novelty is wearing thin by this WINTER BREAK Edition. I found this test to be the least challenging, because the answers are so obviously NOT obvious. These are not lateral thinking problems. Approach the problems from every angle: shake the phone; touch the actual timer; and hit the back button to get rid of the ANNOYING advertisements.
